data.description: PRICE UPDATE and Lender Incentives offered!! Don't miss this beautiful ALL BRICK home with extras!! Open floor plan downstairs featuring hardwood flooring, heavy trim work and built ins around the gas fireplace. The vaulted ceiling and open stair case are nice touches in this beautiful main living area. The kitchen has great flow for cooking and entertaining and offers both an island and desk, quartz counters and stainless appliances  Primary bedroom on main with en-suite (separate shower/soaker tub) and large walk in closet. A full dining room and half bath are also present on the main level. Two guest bedrooms are upstairs with an additional bonus space (currently used as office) and full bathroom with double sink. Back yard features a covered aggregate patio with fan and small barn for storage. Convenient location with easy access to I24. This home has been immaculately maintained by the sellers and is move in ready. BRAND NEW ROOF!!
